scene.message:
Yukino: The Snow Queens of{nl}
ages past lived their school{nl}
lives in the old building —{nl}
is that why it's changed?{waitkey}{clearbox}Which means the demons' power{nl}
has grown even greater than{nl}
before.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: What a nasty vibe.{waitkey}{clearbox}It's an old building to begin{nl}
with, and it's frozen over,{nl}
and the footsteps echo like{nl}
crazy.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: They say old schools{nl}
are steeped in all sorts of{nl}
memories spanning many{nl}
generations.{waitkey}{clearbox}I only hope they don't have{nl}
a bad influence.{waitkey}{ret}
